+{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01TXkrySNfuuv574tteCjhvd","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tasks complete. Here's a summary of what was built:\n\n## Architecture\n\nThe system is organized into 7 source files centered around the **permission engine** as the core concern:\n\n- **`src/types.ts`** - Type definitions for User, Folder, Document, Permission, ActivityLogEntry\n- **`src/store.ts`** - In-memory store using Maps and arrays, with ID generation\n- **`src/permissions.ts`** - The core permission engine with hierarchical resolution: checks direct permissions, then walks up the folder tree. The most permissive role wins across all paths (direct share + folder share + ancestor folder share)\n- **`src/auth.ts`** - Registration, login (returns Bearer tokens), and auth middleware\n- **`src/folders.ts`** - CRUD for folders with nested hierarchy support\n- **`src/documents.ts`** - CRUD for documents with permission-gated access\n- **`src/sharing.ts`** - Share resources with role assignment (viewer/editor/owner)\n- **`src/activity.ts`** - Activity logging for document CRUD and sharing events\n- **`src/app.ts`** - Exports `createApp()` wiring everything together\n\n## API Routes\n\n| Method | Route | Description |\n|--------|-------|-------------|\n| POST | `/auth/register` | Register user |\n| POST | `/auth/login` | Login, get token |\n| POST/GET/PUT/DELETE | `/folders[/:id]` | Folder CRUD |\n| POST/GET/PUT/DELETE | `/documents[/:id]` | Document CRUD |\n| POST | `/share` | Share a resource |\n| GET | `/share/:resourceType/:resourceId` | Get permissions |\n| GET | `/activity` | Activity log (filterable) |\n\n## Key Design Decisions\n\n- **Permission inheritance**: Folder permissions cascade to child folders and contained documents via ancestor traversal\n- **Most permissive wins**: When multiple permission paths exist (e.g., folder editor + doc viewer), the highest role applies\n- **Editor sharing**: Editors can share with viewer/editor roles; only owners can assign the owner role\n- **48 tests** covering auth, folders, documents, sharing/permissions, and activity logging\n\n## Validation Results\n\n- `npm run build` - passes\n- `npm run lint` - passes  \n- `npm test` - 48/48 tests pass"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":426,"cache_read_input_tokens":37391,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":426},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"250c190c-1e5e-4f4f-a3b9-a29f16af91a5","uuid":"7f4a75da-273e-455e-b638-8b5e294b1f1b"}
